oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dugger Family Home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Dugger house at Maple and Cedar Streets. Shown are the Dugger girls.
The Dugger house was constructed in approximately 1905. The home later became the Moreland house.
